Class DefaultXAction

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultCustomizerAction

    public class DefaultXAction
extends AbstractXAction
    Provides an empty actionPerformed method body. Usefull for JCheckBox and JToggleButton, if they are only listening to ItemEvents.
